{"tid":1480831,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"面書機器，全面進場！","createTime":"2019-08-17T12:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T13:38:57.000Z","uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa95582dc0c98fc1c97c1b4c856fd3b69531d16d","tid":1480831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157958576037448&amp;id=105259197447&amp;__tn__=%2AW-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157958576037448%26id%3D105259197447%26__tn__%3D%252AW-R&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=a3639743\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157958576037448&amp;id=105259197447&amp;__tn__=%2AW-R</a><br />\n<br />\n入面留言既全部都係bot<br />\n一㩒入去非常乾淨<br />\n得頭像同cover<br />\n呢類bot因為冇正常使用痕跡<br />\n只要好多人檢舉做bot就可以連根拔起咁剷除<br />\n需要大家幫手！！！！<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n每個連登仔2-3個假acct係基本裝備<br />\n即刻同我申請 入去屌藍絲！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>延伸閱讀</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">請離開連登，離開同溫層。連登太多頭腦，欠缺手腳。全部同我入黎申請分身ac！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439811</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登太多計策，全部都係「搵人同我&hellip;」，結果全部都冇人做。<br />\n<br />\n如今連登欠缺落手做既人，例如隔離post狗竇白布需要報消防，正皮1000人，推post800人，我敢講，真係去電話亭報消防既一個人都冇，覺唔覺得自己羞恥呀香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登生產力急跌，恥笑post開始多，日常post都開始多，證明軍心渙散。如果有貢獻總生產總值，連登仔係零呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重新提醒各位連登仔，呢場仗如果輸咗，以後出街都要活在恐懼之中，係街唔敢高談闊論自己立場，著黑色衫要諗諗，戴口罩帶遮要諗諗，去茶餐廳唔敢講相關話題怕藍絲加料。<br />\n<br />\n我係共產黨，第一時間就會清算連登，有ac既全部都要分批入再教育營，懲教所咁毒打，逐個逐個打傻仔針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n即刻落車！唔好係架車度！<br />\n唔好再圍爐！請立即離開同溫層面對戰場，藍絲page已經開始運用大數據投放廣告，我地要立即申請fb分身ac迎戰，人肉向藍絲宣導傳教。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n懶人傳送門<br />\n申請Gmail<br />\n<a href=\"https://accounts.google.com/signup/v2/webcreateaccount?service=mail&amp;continue=https://mail.google.com/mail/&amp;ltmpl=ecobh&amp;btmpl=mobile&amp;dsh=S403491953:1565423438108887&amp;gmb=exp&amp;biz=false&amp;flowName=GlifWebSignIn&amp;flowEntry=SignUp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.google.com%2Fsignup%2Fv2%2Fwebcreateaccount%3Fservice%3Dmail%26continue%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fmail.google.com%2Fmail%2F%26ltmpl%3Decobh%26btmpl%3Dmobile%26dsh%3DS403491953%3A1565423438108887%26gmb%3Dexp%26biz%3Dfalse%26flowName%3DGlifWebSignIn%26flowEntry%3DSignUp&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=1899e6b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://accounts.google.com/signup/v2/webcreateaccount?service=mail&amp;continue=https://mail.google.com/mail/&amp;ltmpl=ecobh&amp;btmpl=mobile&amp;dsh=S403491953:1565423438108887&amp;gmb=exp&amp;biz=false&amp;flowName=GlifWebSignIn&amp;flowEntry=SignUp</a><br />\n<br />\n申請facebook AC<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/reg/?cid=103&amp;refsrc=https://m.facebook.com/&amp;soft=hjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Freg%2F%3Fcid%3D103%26refsrc%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%26soft%3Dhjk&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=e8a79a11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/reg/?cid=103&amp;refsrc=https://m.facebook.com/&amp;soft=hjk</a><br />\n<br />\n長輩頭像<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=頭像+長輩&amp;tbm=isch&amp;ved=2ahUKEwium8mk6ffjAhXMAqYKHW1iBoIQ2-cCegQIABAC&amp;oq=頭像+長輩&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-wiz-img.3...6195.7640..7820...0.0..0.0.0.......0....1.abCfyPJf2xw&amp;ei=3ndOXa60LMyFmAXtxJmQCA&amp;bih=553&amp;biw=375&amp;client=safari&amp;prmd=imnv&amp;hl=en-gb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%E9%A0%AD%E5%83%8F%2B%E9%95%B7%E8%BC%A9%26tbm%3Disch%26ved%3D2ahUKEwium8mk6ffjAhXMAqYKHW1iBoIQ2-cCegQIABAC%26oq%3D%E9%A0%AD%E5%83%8F%2B%E9%95%B7%E8%BC%A9%26gs_l%3Dmobile-gws-wiz-img.3...6195.7640..7820...0.0..0.0.0.......0....1.abCfyPJf2xw%26ei%3D3ndOXa60LMyFmAXtxJmQCA%26bih%3D553%26biw%3D375%26client%3Dsafari%26prmd%3Dimnv%26hl%3Den-gb&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=df63e87c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=頭像+長輩&amp;tbm=isch&amp;ved=2ahUKEwium8mk6ffjAhXMAqYKHW1iBoIQ2-cCegQIABAC&amp;oq=頭像+長輩&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-wiz-img.3...6195.7640..7820...0.0..0.0.0.......0....1.abCfyPJf2xw&amp;ei=3ndOXa60LMyFmAXtxJmQCA&amp;bih=553&amp;biw=375&amp;client=safari&amp;prmd=imnv&amp;hl=en-gb</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進階+<br />\n<br />\nFd list問題<br />\n申請完請加<br />\nZhong kwok wan<br />\nZhang Simon<br />\n加friend list入面既人<br />\n然後夠15個人就可以unfd我 <br />\n*唔好貪心一次過加太多人 否則會要求提供電話<br />\n<br />\nApp<br />\n有好多副廠app可以替代 自己搵 <br />\n或者down多個瀏覽器長期log in</span>"},{"pid":"67ab0f711a0d8ffc17fa8983b04506e312f047f4","tid":1480831,"uid":42691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:54:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\">如何向藍絲宣導</span><br />\n每個藍絲都會有極端性格<br />\n不管你選擇了以下哪一種方式去宣導藍絲<br />\n都必須視乎情況：<br />\n<br />\n留言前問一問自己 假若自己係藍絲<br />\n會唔會信 會唔會好假膠<br />\n句留言會唔會太似反話<br />\n需要極高語言技巧及演技<br />\n如果冇信心既請採用下文最後既直屌模式<br />\n<br />\n用咩方法冇所謂<br />\n重要的是結果<br />\n我們要贏 我們要拉攏淺藍<br />\n<br />\n以下例子為真實取材<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.以藍制藍<br />\n以超越藍絲既變態思維 <br />\n嚇怕佢地/培養佢地走火入魔<br />\n從而令理性藍絲反感<br />\n<br />\n有人說：「咁都睇到係胸襲，黃尸真係xxxxx」<br />\n解答：<br />\n「不就是摸了幾下」<br />\n「摸咗又點 警察叫極都唔走！抵死啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.指鹿為馬<br />\n少女被捕<br />\n有人說：「可能是男扮女」<br />\n呢個時候手足要立即讚好 讚到佢變top為止<br />\n當讚好數目有返咁上下 <br />\n我地就可以走出黎屌柒佢<br />\n或者手足主動留言 <br />\n我地會馬上意會配合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.分化模式<br />\n分化警察政府：<br />\n「警察是無辜的 請政府不要再推他們去死 」<br />\n分化前線指揮：<br />\n「屌你老母冷氣白衫」/「散仔衝動累事」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.消毒模式<br />\n藍絲回覆好多虛假指控<br />\n只要用證據車落佢地塊面度就ok了<br />\n理性藍絲睇到自然會分析<br />\n*建議貼圖 不用多花唇舌<br />\n<br />\n有人說：「&hellip;好多曱甴」<br />\n屋企污糟先有曱甴，而唔係有曱甴而污糟<br />\n或者<br />\n蘇乞兒ending.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.直屌模式<br />\n希望唔好用 <br />\n因為藍絲普遍要面<br />\n唔係個個都可以被直屌而頓悟<br />\n除非佢冇得救 <br />\n咁就可以做箭靶、警醒理性藍絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n希望大家夠定力<br />\n唔好染上上面既陋習 各位睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2083c897d05d99be974e0d24ae52b0714d0bfb","tid":1480831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ee2f565803bca135c1a1b61b810475f8c15e13b","tid":1480831,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"檢舉不如直接洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89c520b7c365628079aeb761e624b47385110f8","tid":1480831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ee2f565803bca135c1a1b61b810475f8c15e13b","tid":1480831,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"檢舉不如直接洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"人地幾千個like 推唔上去top"},{"pid":"4cd53339f68d564a1a7371fcb9438bd125b1ab27","tid":1480831,"uid":297357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqARc2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqARc2e.jpg&h=43c10fb1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}